{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"pesky-eye-pad","description":"# S7 — End-to-end proof + backup/restore drill + monitoring + runbooks\n\n## Why\nProve the whole gate works end-to-end and that freeze-and-restore is real. This is the\ndogfood-readiness checkpoint for d251 (P1 integrity proven on a real change; P3 restore\nproven). The full four-pass dogfood is b744-WS6.\n\n## What\n- E2E proof: push a change -> the bot reviews + votes `LLM-Review` -> submit (whole-topic)\n  -> replicate -> the change appears on GitHub `main`; AND a direct GitHub push / PR-merge to\n  `main` is rejected.\n- Backup/restore: verify DLM snapshots + a `$site_path` snapshot (git/ + etc/ incl.\n  secure.config + ssh_host keys; index/ + cache/ excluded, taken from a snapshot/stop window,\n  not a naive hot tar); run a restore-from-IaC drill and record the achieved RTO; confirm\n  merged code is safe on GitHub (RPO = only in-flight reviews at risk).\n- Monitoring: CloudWatch basic + an alarm on \"gate down\" (Gerrit/MCP unreachable) so an\n  outage — which freezes `main` — is noticed.\n- Runbooks: provision/restore + the one-minor-at-a-time Gerrit upgrade.\n\n## Scope\nIn: the e2e proof, the restore drill, monitoring, runbooks. Out: the full four-pass\ndogfood (b744-WS6).\n\n## Files\n- `infra/runbooks/*.md`, `infra/terraform/monitoring.tf`, an e2e test script under `infra/tests/`\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] E2E proof passes: a test change is reviewed + voted + submitted in Gerrit and appears on\n      GitHub `main`; a direct GitHub push / PR-merge to `main` is rejected.\n- [ ] A restore-from-backup drill succeeds (rebuild from Terraform + restore `$site_path`)\n      within the recorded RTO target; merged history is confirmed intact on GitHub.\n- [ ] A gate-down condition raises an alert (CloudWatch alarm on Gerrit/MCP health).\n- [ ] Provision/restore + Gerrit upgrade runbooks exist under `infra/runbooks/`.","id":"3178-7e4c-b571-473c","parent_id":"d251-05e1-eb55-43b2","priority":2,"tags":["infra","e2e","ops"],"ticket_type":"story","title":"infra: S7 — End-to-end proof + backup/restore drill + monitoring + runbooks"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782685510061557001,"uuid":"3655224e-f29a-4c85-b4e9-1dc8a08afc56"}